{
  "stem": "11744.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He'll just be put away in prison.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it took me a tremendous amount of research to find out where he was, and I finally did, and this I couldn't do anything about.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was there for about four months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did-- it happened three times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's only the first time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first time it happened, I really didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know what I could do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, when he got back, then he abandoned completely any business or anything, and he went completely in the resistance.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But not before he took out from that store hundreds of-- of blankets and woolen socks and everything that he needed for the resistance where the kids were going there in the-- went in the summer, and they didn't have any clothes or anything for the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so everything he could take out of that store, he did, and he brought it to-- he was like a quartermaster of the resistance at that time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's no such a thing as joining.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, that question has been asked to me so many times.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no such a thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you knew somebody who was doing something, and you wanted to help him or her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got confronted with the-- with people who were doing the sneaking out of children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so here and there I was find myself having a few children on my hands and tried to find a place to put them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we established a kind of a chain, being tremendously helped by the priest and the nuns who were taking them into monasteries or in their own quarters until they could place them in farm.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was really-- the women were mainly involved in that.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
